com.onwbp.adaptation
Class AdaptationName

java.lang.Object
  com.onwbp.adaptation.AdaptationName
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdaptationReference
public abstract class AdaptationName
extends Object

Identifies a data set or record. Several implementations are provided:

  • Public reference: a string that identifies a data set or record in a persistent manner, and can be viewed in EBX5 user interface (see AdaptationReference);
  • Internal key: a composite key identifying either a data set or a record, designed for cache performance and for holding a UUID. It is not part of public API.

A data set or record can be retrieved by calling method AdaptationHome.findAdaptationOrNull(AdaptationName).

See Also:
AdaptationHome.findAdaptationOrNull(AdaptationName)
